his money?

4
00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:07.976
We didn't kill your dad
any more than you did.

5
00:00:08.008 --> 00:00:09.142
We're gonna
clear our names.

6
00:00:09.176 --> 00:00:10.578
We're a lot of things
but we're not cops.

7
00:00:10.612 --> 00:00:12.680
But whoever is behind it
is gonna make sure

8
00:00:12.714 --> 00:00:13.815
