Aha. Ha.

37
00:03:07.989 --> 00:03:09.189
Ahh.

38
00:03:10.390 --> 00:03:13.493
- You OK?
- I'm great.

39
00:03:13.528 --> 00:03:14.962
Then I assume there's

40
00:03:14.996 --> 00:03:17.799
