who needed it.

73
00:04:23.330 --> 00:04:25.032
Well. I look forward
to reading all about it

74
00:04:25.066 --> 00:04:26.466
in this little. uh...

75
00:04:28.970 --> 00:04:32.974
OK. Fine.
Maybe later.

76
00:04:33.007 --> 00:04:36.077
Anything in there that
can help us hunt down
the Court of Owls?

77
00:04:36.110 --> 00:04:37.845
