conspiracy theories.

78
00:04:37.879 --> 00:04:40.648
It's not exactly
a how-to on catching
my dad's killers.

79
00:04:40.681 --> 00:04:42.449
Nothing concrete.
I can't help thinking

80
00:04:42.482 --> 00:04:43.785
the most important pages
were the ones

81
00:04:43.818 --> 00:04:44.852
