82
00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:50.725
Well. um. I have an
AP Bio exam to cram for.

83
00:04:50.758 --> 00:04:53.360
It's gonna do to me what
the Mutant Leader couldn't.

84
00:05:01.102 --> 00:05:02.970
Does it say in here
why daddy didn't

85
00:05:03.004 --> 00:05:05.506
pick you to be
his sidekick?

86
00:05:05.540 --> 00:05:07.542
I mean. Bat-points
for him not just doing

87
00:05:07.575 --> 00:05:09.677
the whole nepotism thing.
and clearly.

88
00:05:09.710 --> 00:05:12.280
Little Bird is qualified.
but I mean. come on.

89
00:05:12.312 --> 00:05:14.649
It's gotta sting. like.
a tiny. bitty bit

90
00:05:14.682 --> 00:05:16.517
that he just handed
his whole legacy to

91
00:05:16.551 --> 00:05:18.586
some random stranger. right?

92
00:05:20.254 --> 00:05:22.489
I'm sure he had his reasons.

93
00:05:24.592 --> 00:05:26.761
OK.

94
00:05:30.598 --> 00:05:32.365
After the Mutant
Gang's reign of terror

95
00:05:32.399 --> 00:05:33.768
following the death of Batman.

96
00:05:33.801 --> 00:05:36.237
Gotham can sleep a bit
easier tonight

97
00:05:36.270 --> 00:05:38.539
now that Vernon Wagner.
also known by his

98
00:05:38.573 --> 00:05:40.641
nom de crime
"The Mutant Leader."

99
00:05:40.675 --> 00:05:43.511
is safely
and. given his sheer size.

100
00:05:43.544 --> 00:05:46.180
snugly behind bars.

101
00:05:46.214 --> 00:05:48.649
Celebrating this victory
was Mayor Hill.

102
00:05:48.683 --> 00:05:51.819
On my order.
the brave men of the GCPD

103
00:05:51.853 --> 00:05:53.521
have captured
the degenerate leader

104
00:05:53.554 --> 00:05:55.923
of the Mutant Gang.
and starting today.

105
00:05:55.957 --> 00:05:58.860
we're deploying 100 more
officers to hunt down

106
00:05:58.893 --> 00:06:00.393
