110
00:06:09.770 --> 00:06:12.273
Mr. Mayor! Mr. Mayor!

111
00:06:12.306 --> 00:06:13.574
Is that really gonna work?

112
00:06:14.842 --> 00:06:17.678
Does it make the streets
of Gotham safer

113
00:06:17.712 --> 00:06:19.446
when you pressure.
one of my ADAs into

114
00:06:19.479 --> 00:06:21.549
