against Brody March?

115
00:06:21.582 --> 00:06:23.416
Kid clearly
learned his lesson.

116
00:06:23.450 --> 00:06:25.586
Came down to the GCPD
to confess.

117
00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:28.990
