118
00:06:29.023 --> 00:06:32.093
Right. because it was
donated to your
campaign coffers.

119
00:06:33.728 --> 00:06:37.430
How big a contribution
did Lincoln March make
to your re-election fund?

120
00:06:37.464 --> 00:06:39.233
Why? You trying to figure
out how much you gotta

121
00:06:39.267 --> 00:06:41.102
raise to beat me
