122
00:06:41.135 --> 00:06:43.403
Or are you still
too scared to get
in the race?

123
00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:45.940
I'll see you at the gala.

124
00:06:57.551 --> 00:07:00.755
"GCPD Captures
Mutant Gang Leader."

125
