139
00:07:43.531 --> 00:07:44.732
Hey. Steph.

140
00:07:46.133 --> 00:07:47.368
Um--

141
00:07:47.401 --> 00:07:49.003
Carrie.

142
00:07:52.873 --> 00:07:55.776
Well. I don't know
what's more surprising--

143
00:07:55.810 --> 00:07:58.379
