in other ways. Trust me.

150
00:08:15.563 --> 00:08:17.398
Anyway. the reason
I'm here in the--

151
00:08:17.431 --> 00:08:20.468
what'd you call this place?
The...library?

152
00:08:20.501 --> 00:08:22.803
Ha. Is because
I wanted to ask you

153
00:08:22.837 --> 00:08:25.706
