164
00:08:48.062 --> 00:08:51.298
Brody lied to the police
about hacking the banks.

165
00:08:51.332 --> 00:08:53.567
For me.
I kind of owe him.

166
00:08:53.601 --> 00:08:55.269
Yeah. I'm with
Brownie on this one.

167
00:08:55.302 --> 00:08:57.738
I mean. you got her into
trouble. he got her out. so.

168
00:08:57.772 --> 00:09:00.174
think that earns her
a ticket to the Brodeo.

169
00:09:00.207 --> 00:09:01.609
Please stay off my side.

170
00:09:01.642 --> 00:09:02.843
And I highly doubt
that me splitting

171
00:09:02.877 --> 00:09:04.445
a cheese platter
with Brody

172
00:09:04.478 --> 00:09:06.580
is your most
pressing concern.

173
00:09:06.614 --> 00:09:08.783
OK. Where are you
on your clue trail?

174
00:09:08.816 --> 00:09:11.185
At a dead end.
But check this out.

175
00:09:11.218 --> 00:09:13.254
My dad wrote about his theory
that the Court of Owls

176
00:09:13.287 --> 00:09:16.190
were hunting the Wayne
family for over 100 years.

177
00:09:16.223 --> 00:09:19.460
Starting with his
great-great-grandfather
Alan Wayne.

178
00:09:19.493 --> 00:09:20.995
But all the accounts
of the time say that

179
00:09:21.028 --> 00:09:22.997
he drowned in a sewer
when he accidentally

180
00:09:23.030 --> 00:09:24.732
fell into a manhole.

181
00:09:24.765 --> 00:09:26.734
Newspapers attributed it
to dementia but

182
00:09:26.767 --> 00:09:28.469
here's where
it gets interesting.

183
00:09:28.503 --> 00:09:29.937
Witnesses at
the time said that

184
00:09:29.970 --> 00:09:31.338
he was
last heard screaming.

185
00:09:31.372 --> 00:09:33.774
"The owls are in my house."

186
00:09:33.808 --> 00:09:35.609
That can't be
a coincidence.

187
00:09:35.643 --> 00:09:38.145
- Yeah.
- So. what now?

188
00:09:38.179 --> 00:09:40.815
Well. I know what
the World's Greatest
Detective would do.

189
00:09:40.848 --> 00:09:43.751
Can't solve the last murder.
go back to the first.

190
00:09:43.784 --> 00:09:45.886
If the Court did kill
Alan Wayne.

191
00:09:45.920 --> 00:09:48.022
maybe looking through
his cold case

192
00:09:48.055 --> 00:09:50.024
will help us prove
they killed my dad.

193
00:09:50.057 --> 00:09:51.759
Figure out how
they did it.
maybe see if

194
00:09:51.792 --> 00:09:53.562
we can find out
who was involved.

195
00:09:53.594 --> 00:09:54.762
It's a long shot.

196
00:09:54.795 --> 00:09:56.497
All cold cases
are long shots.

197
00:09:56.531 --> 00:09:57.898
But if you could
get your hands

198
00:09:57.932 --> 00:09:59.534
on the original case file.
maybe we could

199
00:09:59.568 --> 00:10:01.536
find something the police
missed back then.

200
00:10:01.570 --> 00:10:04.105
Yeah. if the original
case file

201
00:10:04.138 --> 00:10:07.174
wasn't collecting cobwebs
in the GCPD basement.

202
00:10:07.208 --> 00:10:09.043
- Right.
- Can't exactly just

203
00:10:09.076 --> 00:10:10.644
go and check it out.

204
00:10:10.678 --> 00:10:13.013
No. but we could steal it.

205
00:10:14.748 --> 00:10:16.083
- How?
- Why don't ya

206
00:10:16.117 --> 00:10:18.085
leave that to the thieves
to figure out?

207
00:10:31.699 --> 00:10:33.667
In a stunning development.

208
00:10:33.701 --> 00:10:36.203
the Mutant Gang has now
claimed responsibility for

209
00:10:36.237 --> 00:10:39.406
last night's downing
of a GCPD airship

210
00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:41.543
that crashed into Ace Chemicals.

211
00:10:41.576 --> 00:10:44.411
causing widespread fires
that at this moment

212
00:10:44.445 --> 00:10:45.813
have not been contained.

213
00:10:45.846 --> 00:10:47.549
If not for the brave efforts

214
00:10:47.582 --> 00:10:49.016
of Gotham's firefighters.

215
00:10:49.049 --> 00:10:50.619
toxic fumes
would have surely been

216
00:10:50.651 --> 00:10:52.153
unleashed upon the city.

217
00:10:52.186 --> 00:10:54.688
The motive behind
this senseless act of terror

218
00:10:54.722 --> 00:10:56.490
became clear when
the Mutant Gang

219
00:10:56.525 --> 00:10:58.826
