would be proud of you.
but I sure am.

227
00:11:24.018 --> 00:11:26.588
Wait.
I'm going with you.

228
00:11:26.621 --> 00:11:29.490
This is my mess
and I'm gonna clean it up

229
00:11:29.524 --> 00:11:30.724
before anyone else
gets hurt.

230
00:11:30.758 --> 00:11:32.193
You don't have
to do it alone.

231
00:11:32.226 --> 00:11:34.461
You were my dad's backup.
Let me be yours.

232
00:11:34.495 --> 00:11:37.064
I appreciate the offer.
I really do.

233
00:11:37.097 --> 00:11:38.999
But you have enough to do
trying to clear your names.

234
00:11:39.033 --> 00:11:40.401
Not until we can
jailbreak that

235
00:11:40.434 --> 00:11:41.802
Alan Wayne file
