out of breadcrumbs.

237
00:11:43.437 --> 00:11:45.806
You know we made a pretty
good team against the Talon.

238
00:11:45.839 --> 00:11:48.175
Maybe we treat the
Mutant Gang to a bit
of that teamwork.

239
00:11:48.209 --> 00:11:49.810
